title: Accidentally bought illegal items of Wish

comments.comment: So believe it or not,  those EXACT spring knives you looked at got me arrested. I ordered one thinking it was a plastic replica. It was like $9 or something got it shipped to my home in London. And I got a letter saying that it had been taken away by borderforce or something. So I ignored it as it said ' If you need it,  you can come collect it' which sounds like a trap. About 4 weeks later 2 undercover police knock on the door and search my home thinking I'm running some whole operation.  Got arrested. Got questioned , got de-arrested. Life goes on. RIP $9
